SkillDec.SourceString: 攻击附带强力灰噬效果，需要提高对应元素抗性或避免被命中。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Attacks come with a powerful Graying Bite effect. Increase corresponding elemental resistance or avoid being hit.

SkillDec.SourceString: BOSS生命血量越低减伤越高，BOSS变为处决机制，可用破盾高的武器对其破盾并处决，处决伤害无视怪物减伤，并与攻击和抗性和增伤有关。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: The lower the boss's HP, the greater its damage reduction. The boss can then be executed. Use weapons with high shatter to break its shield and execute it. Execution damage ignores the boss's damage reduction and is affected by the Wanderer's ATK, resistance, and damage boost.

SkillDec.SourceString: 获得地狱烈焰技能，大部分攻击会在地面留下大面积持续燃烧，避免进入燃烧区域。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Gain the Infernal Flames skill. The majority of the boss's attacks will leave a large area on the ground that burns continuously. Avoid entering the burning areas.

SkillDec.SourceString: 场景随机生成大爆破，被命中会造成致命伤害，并在区域留下地狱烈焰。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Large random explosions will occur in the area, dealing lethal damage upon hit and leaving Infernal Flames in the area.

SkillDec.SourceString: 弗丽嘉护盾值大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frigg's shield strength greatly increases.

SkillDec.SourceString: 弗丽嘉每次命中玩家获得伤害提升，可叠加。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frigg gains a damage boost each time she lands a hit. This effect can stack.

SkillDec.SourceString: 弗丽嘉开启狂暴模式，所有行动速度大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frigg enters Rampage Mode, greatly increasing her speed.

SkillDec.SourceString: 弗丽嘉进入极限状态，所有行动速度获得提升，会在脚下地面留下霜冻，碰到霜冻的玩家会受到伤害并被减速，最高叠加3层。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frigg enters Extreme Mode, increasing her speed and leaving frost under her feet. If you touch the frost, you will take damage and be slowed, which can be stacked up to 3 times.

SkillDec.SourceString: 瓦尔基里所有行动速度提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Increase speed of all of Valkyrie's actions.

SkillDec.SourceString: 瓦尔基里每秒可以免疫一次伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Valkyrie is immune to damage 1 time every second.

SkillDec.SourceString: 瓦尔基里每隔一段时间会在自身周围地面留下可以被破坏的电极，电极每隔一定时间会对范围内释放圆形电流。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Valkyrie leaves destructible electrodes on the ground around it at regular intervals. These electrodes periodically emit a circular electrical current in the surrounding area.

SkillDec.SourceString: 每隔一段时间，瓦尔基里会对周围降下落雷，落雷会造成致命伤害，并且进入感电状态，感电状态受到雷属性攻击命中会触电。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Valkyrie summons lightning bolts around it at regular intervals, dealing lethal damage and electrifying targets. When an electrified target is hit by a volt attack, chain lightning is triggered.

SkillDec.SourceString: 科尔顿每秒会对选中目标触发敌意，每层敌意使目标减速，最多叠加5层，持续5秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Culton triggers Hostility on the selected target every second. Each stack of Hostility slows the target for 5 seconds, stacking up to 5 times.

SkillDec.SourceString: 科尔顿每隔30秒使周围玩家陷入混乱往反向移动，持续15秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: For every 30 seconds, Culton induces chaos, reversing Wanderers' movement for 15 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 科尔顿每损失10%最大生命值进入3秒无敌状态。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Culton enters an invincible state for 3s each time he loses a certain amount of HP.

SkillDec.SourceString: 科尔顿最终阶段会召唤红色石柱，每个石柱会给科尔顿增加20%增伤和减伤，可让科尔顿撞毁石柱让增益失效。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: In the final phase, Culton summons red pillars. Each pillar increases Culton's damage boost and damage reduction by 20%. Make Culton collide with the pillars to disable the buffs.

SkillDec.SourceString: 铁俑攻击有一定概率给目标添加5秒破招效果，破招效果内霸体失效。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Iron Tomb's attacks have a certain chance to inflict a 5-second Countermove effect, disabling the target's hyperbody for its duration.

SkillDec.SourceString: 铁俑每隔20秒会获得自身损失的最大生命值减伤，持续20秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 20 seconds, Iron Tomb gains damage reduction based on its Max HP lost for 20 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 铁俑每8秒攻击附带一次致残效果，命中非坚毅目标大幅降低其伤害和被治疗效果，持续8秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 8 seconds, Iron Tomb's attacks inflict a Maim effect, significantly reducing the damage dealt and healing received on non-Fortitude targets for 8 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 铁俑每20秒会随机对范围内2名玩家进行链接，被链接的玩家降低30%最终伤害并且每个提供铁俑30%最终伤害，远离铁俑可中断链接。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 20 seconds, Iron Tomb randomly links 2 players within range, reducing their final damage by 30%; each linked player provides a 30% increase in Iron Tomb's final damage. Moving away from Iron Tomb can break the link.

SkillDec.SourceString: 盖亚每次命中非坚毅目标会给目标添加碎骨状态，碎骨叠加到20层会触发骨折，极大降低造成的伤害，持续10秒
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Gaia inflicts Bonecrush on targets without Fortitude with each hit. At 20 stacks, the debuff triggers Cripple, massively reducing their damage dealt for 10s.

SkillDec.SourceString: 盖亚每15秒会随机点名一个目标，该目标5秒后每秒对大范围内除自己外友军造成多次致命伤害。持续5秒
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 15 seconds, Gaia randomly selects a target. After 5 seconds, the selected target inflicts wide-area lethal damage every second to all allies except themselves for 5 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 被盖亚命中后会被减速，最多叠加2层，持续5秒
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Targets hit by Gaia are slowed for 5 seconds, stacking up to 2 times.

SkillDec.SourceString: 盖亚被破盾后10秒内每秒会对周围造成大范围的伤害，被该伤害命中后会叠加15%易伤，最多3层，持续10秒
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Gaia deals wide-area damage every second for 10s after the shield is shattered. Targets hit are inflicted with 15% Vulnerability for 10s, up to 3 stacks.

SkillDec.SourceString: 丝薇缇每25秒会对周围随机2-4个目标释放罚站，BUFF持续5秒后若目标正在进行任何行为则会造成伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 25 seconds, Sweetie casts Penalty on 2–4 random nearby targets. The targets will take damage if they engage in any actions within 5 seconds of receiving Penalty.

SkillDec.SourceString: 丝薇缇所有行动速度提升，并且周围所有目标行动速度下降。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Increase Sweetie's movement speed, and decrease the movement speed of all nearby targets.

SkillDec.SourceString: 丝薇缇每15秒随机选择场上一名目标使其每秒受到巨大伤害（优先选择坚毅目标），持续15秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 15 seconds, Sweetie randomly selects a target on the field to inflict massive damage every second for 15 seconds, prioritizing targets with Fortitude Resonance.

SkillDec.SourceString: 丝薇缇会链接场上所有我方目标，每个目标会损失其他目标受到伤害百分比伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Sweetie chains all Wanderer-allied targets on the field. Each target will suffer damage proportional to the percentage of damage received by other chained targets.

SkillDec.SourceString: 姹鲛每损失一定生命值，攻击力将会获得提高。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Whenever Merbelle loses a certain amount of HP, its attack will increase.

SkillDec.SourceString: 姹鲛拥有护盾时获得高额减伤，并且护盾值大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: When Merbelle has a shield, gain additional damage reduction and greatly increase shield strength.

SkillDec.SourceString: 姹鲛每次伤害添加急冻状态，当累计15层急冻状态会清除急冻状态并大幅减速，持续6秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Each time Merbelle deals damage, inflicts a stack of Flashfreeze. When Flashfreeze stacks 15 times, stacks clear and the Wanderer is greatly slowed for 6 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 姹鲛每隔15秒会对一个目标释放冰柱造成巨大伤害，冰柱会停留在场上，每隔10秒回复姹鲛3%最大生命值，冰柱可通过多次攻击摧毁。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Merbelle unleashes an ice pillar at a target every 15 seconds, dealing huge damage. The ice pillar remains on the field, restoring 3% of Merbelle's Max HP every 10 seconds. The ice pillar can be destroyed by multiple attacks.

SkillDec.SourceString: 急冻机甲周围会持续生成立场生成器，每个生成器给急冻机甲提供减伤，可以通过多次攻击击破。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frost Bot continuously generates positioning generators around it. Each generator provides damage reduction to Frost Bot and can be shattered through multiple attacks.

SkillDec.SourceString: 急冻机甲会对自身进行修复，缓慢回复生命值。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frost Bot will repair itself, slowly recovering HP.

SkillDec.SourceString: 大幅提升急冻机甲行动速度。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Greatly increase the movement speed of Frost Bot.

SkillDec.SourceString: 急冻机甲每秒会对自身周围释放强力寒气，并持续减速周围目标。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frost Bot releases a powerful chill around itself every second, continuously Slowing nearby targets.

SkillDec.SourceString: 攻击附带强力灰噬效果，需要提高对应元素抗性或避免被命中。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Attacks come with a powerful Graying Bite effect. Increase corresponding elemental resistance or avoid being hit.

SkillDec.SourceString: 阿波菲斯变为处决机制，可用破盾高的武器对其破盾并处决。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Apophis can be executed. Use weapons with high shatter to break its shield and execute it.

SkillDec.SourceString: 大幅提升阿波菲斯行动速度。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Greatly increase the movement speed of Apophis.

SkillDec.SourceString: 阿波菲斯周围目标霸体失效。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Nullify the hyperbody status of targets around Apophis.

SkillDec.SourceString: 米诺陶极大降低受到来自主仇恨目标的伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Minotaur significantly reduces damage received from the primary aggro target.

SkillDec.SourceString: 米诺陶变为处决机制，可用破盾高的武器对其破盾并处决。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Minotaur can be executed. Use weapons with high shatter to break its shield and execute it.

SkillDec.SourceString: 米诺陶每隔15秒会随机一个恩赐目标添加毒奶状态，使目标治疗变为同等的伤害。持续10秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 15 seconds, Minotaur randomly selects a target with Benediction, applying Toxicitea, which converts the target's healing into an equivalent amount of damage. Lasts for 10 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 米诺陶每隔15秒会对所有玩家释放检测，若有玩家周围5米内没有其他玩家，该玩家将去除霸体和无敌状态并在90秒内无法添加霸体和无敌状态。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 15 seconds, Minotaur examines all Wanderers. If a Wanderer is found to be within 5 meters without any other Wanderers nearby, that Wanderer will lose their hyperbody and invincibility and will be unable to regain hyperbody or invincibility for 90 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 伦迪尔护盾值大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Greatly increase Rudolph's Shield.

SkillDec.SourceString: 伦迪尔正面获得极大减伤，但背后受到的伤害会提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Rudolph receives a massive damage reduction from the front, but its damage taken from behind is increased.

SkillDec.SourceString: 伦迪尔每隔一定时间会开启5秒大范围幻时。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Rudolph activates a wide-area Phantasia for 5 seconds at set intervals.

SkillDec.SourceString: 伦迪尔开启狂化模式，所有行动速度大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Rudolph enters Rampage Mode, greatly increasing its movement speed.

SkillDec.SourceString: 赛拉芙攻击附带强力灰噬效果。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Seraph's attacks carry an additional Powerful Graying Bite effect.

SkillDec.SourceString: 赛拉芙命中目标后会给15米范围内所有己方单位添加5%最大生命值的生命护盾，无法叠加，持续3秒，最短触发间隔1秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: After Seraph lands a hit on a target, it grants a HP shield to all its friendly units equal to 5% of their respective Max HP. The shield cannot be stacked and lasts for 3 seconds. The minimum trigger interval is 1 second.

SkillDec.SourceString: 赛拉芙命中非坚毅目标后添加制裁，制裁5秒会减少一层，若制裁达到10层则去除霸体和无敌状态并在90秒内无法添加霸体和无敌状态。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: After Seraph hits a non-Fortitude target, Punishments will be added. Punishments will be reduced by 1 stack every 5 seconds. If Punishment stacks reach 10, that Wanderer will lose their hyperbody and invincibility and will be unable to regain hyperbody or invincibility for 90 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 赛拉芙受到致命伤会无敌10秒，并在期间每秒对周围持续造成巨大伤害。触发间隔120秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: When Seraph recevies lethal damage, it becomes invincible for 10 seconds. During that period, it continuously deals a huge amount of damage every second to the surrounding area. The trigger interval is 120 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 索贝克锁定的目标将大幅降低暴击率。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: When Sobek locks onto a target, their critical hit rate is significantly reduced.

SkillDec.SourceString: 索贝克变为处决机制，可用破盾高的武器对其破盾并处决。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Sobek can be executed. Use weapons with high shatter to break its shield and execute it.

SkillDec.SourceString: 索贝克命中非坚毅目标会给目标添加易伤，持续10秒，最多10层。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: When Sobek hits a non-Fortitude target, it applies Vulnerability to the target for 10 seconds, stacking up to 10 times.

SkillDec.SourceString: 索贝克开进入疯狂状态，所有行动速度大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Sobek enters a frenzy state, greatly increasing all speeds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 歌者造成伤害为侵蚀伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: The Singer's attacks inflict Corrosion DMG.

SkillDec.SourceString: 歌者持续对周围造成高额辐射伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: The Singer constantly deals massive Radiation DMG to nearby enemies.

SkillDec.SourceString: 歌者每30秒会身边召唤出一个替身，替身存在时歌者将进入无敌状态。对替身攻击一定次数可消灭替身解除歌者无敌。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: The Singer summons a decoy every 30 seconds, becoming invincible while the decoy exists. Attack the decoy a set number of times to destroy it and dispel the Singer's Invincibility.

SkillDec.SourceString: 歌者每次造成伤害会添加腐蚀效果，腐蚀达到20层会降低目标攻击力和行动速度，持续15秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Whenever dealing damage, the Singer inflicts a stack of Corruption, which, upon reaching 20 stacks, reduces the target's ATK and movement speed for 15 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 耶梦加得所有行为获得加速。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Jormungand gains speed in all actions.

SkillDec.SourceString: 耶梦加得直接斩杀血量低于20%的目标。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Jormungand instantly executes target with less than 20% health.

SkillDec.SourceString: 耶梦加得每隔10秒会对场上所有目标发射穿透光波造成伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 10 seconds, Jormungand fires a piercing light beam, dealing damage to all targets on the field.

SkillDec.SourceString: 耶梦加得自身以及周围怪物受到攻击有概率不会受到伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: There's a chance that Jormungand and nearby monsters won't take damage when attacked.

SkillDec.SourceString: 鬣狗机甲每次攻击会获得一层20%伤害提升过热值，到达5层后会清除过热值回复自己一部分最大生命值。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Hyena Mech gains a 20% damage increase and one stack of Overheat with each attack. Upon reaching 5 Overheat stacks, it resets and restores a portion of its Max HP.

SkillDec.SourceString: 鬣狗机甲的攻击无视目标抗性
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Hyena Mech's attacks ignore the target's resistance.

SkillDec.SourceString: 鬣狗机甲每隔20秒使周围目标生命护盾失效，持续10秒
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Hyena Mech disables the HP shields of surrounding targets every 20s, lasting 10s.

SkillDec.SourceString: 鬣狗机甲会频繁使用机枪扫射，并且扫射范围大幅提升
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Hyena Mech frequently unleashes machine gun sweeps, with its range greatly increased.

SkillDec.SourceString: 南音攻击会随着时间不断提升，受到成功反击后提升攻击将清空。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Nan Yin's ATK increases over time. Successful counterattacks from enemies remove the ATK increased.

SkillDec.SourceString: 南音每隔5秒会使选中目标眩晕2秒，若目标位坚毅则不生效。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Nan Yin stuns the selected target for 2 seconds every 5 seconds, ineffective against targets with Fortitude.

SkillDec.SourceString: 南音额外获得一定减伤，但若被破防会损失大量生命值。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Nan Yin gains additional Damage Reduction, but loses a large amount of HP if shattered.

SkillDec.SourceString: 南音命中目标后会使目标霸体失效，持续10秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Nan Yin negates the target's hyperbody for 10 seconds upon hit.

SkillDec.SourceString: 阿斯拉达每隔一定时间会减少自己受到的伤害，若被破招则减伤会消失。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Asurada periodically gains damage reduction, which is removed when successfully countered.

SkillDec.SourceString: 阿斯拉达命中的目标会降低最大生命值，可叠加3层，持续10秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: When Asurada hits targets, it reduces their Max HP for 10s, stacking up to 3 times.

SkillDec.SourceString: 阿斯拉达命中的目标短时间内无法被治疗。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Asurada prevents targets hit from healing for a short period.

SkillDec.SourceString: 阿斯拉达命中非坚毅目标会对目标进行焚烧，每秒造成百分比最大生命流失，可叠加3层，持续10秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Asurada's hits on non-Fortitude targets sear them, dealing damage based on a percentage of their Max HP every second for 10s, stacking up to 3 times.

SkillDec.SourceString: 巢母拥有较高抗暴能力，若被破防则抗暴能力暂时消失。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: The Hive Mother has high Crit Resistance. If her defenses are shattered, her Crit Resistance will temporarily disappear.

SkillDec.SourceString: 巢母进入战斗会召唤2只狂暴刑徒协助作战，刑徒处于无敌状态，巢母被击败后刑徒会死亡。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Upon entering battle, the Hive Mother will summon 2 Rampage Prisoners to assist in combat. The Prisoners are in an invincible state, and will die once the Hive Mother is defeated.

SkillDec.SourceString: 巢母每隔5秒对锁定目标每秒造成致命伤害，若目标是坚毅则大幅降低该伤害，持续5秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 5 seconds, the Hive Mother inflicts lethal damage every second to the locked-on target for 5 seconds. If the target has Fortitude, this damage is significantly reduced.

SkillDec.SourceString: 巢母每隔15秒检测周围，若周围没有同时存在强攻，均衡，坚毅，恩赐，则巢母所有攻击附带致命伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 15 seconds, the Hive Mother scans her surroundings. If Attack, Balance, Fortitude, and Benediction are not present at the same time, all of the Hive Mother's attacks will inflict lethal damage.

SkillDec.SourceString: 攻击附带强力灰噬效果，需要提高对应元素抗性或避免被命中。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Attacks come with a powerful Graying Bite effect. Increase corresponding elemental resistance or avoid being hit.

SkillDec.SourceString: BOSS生命血量越低减伤越高，BOSS变为处决机制，可用破盾高的武器对其破盾并处决，处决伤害无视怪物减伤，并与攻击和抗性和增伤有关。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: The lower the boss's HP, the greater its damage reduction. The boss can then be executed. Use weapons with high shatter to break its shield and execute it. Execution damage ignores the boss's damage reduction and is affected by the Wanderer's ATK, resistance, and damage boost.

SkillDec.SourceString: 获得地狱烈焰技能，大部分攻击会在地面留下大面积持续燃烧，避免进入燃烧区域。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Gain the Infernal Flames skill. The majority of the boss's attacks will leave a large area on the ground that burns continuously. Avoid entering the burning areas.

SkillDec.SourceString: 场景随机生成大爆破，被命中会造成致命伤害，并在区域留下地狱烈焰。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Large random explosions will occur in the area, dealing lethal damage upon hit and leaving Infernal Flames in the area.

SkillDec.SourceString: 弗丽嘉护盾值大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frigg's shield strength greatly increases.

SkillDec.SourceString: 弗丽嘉每次命中玩家获得伤害提升，可叠加。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frigg gains a damage boost each time she lands a hit. This effect can stack.

SkillDec.SourceString: 弗丽嘉开启狂暴模式，所有行动速度大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frigg enters Rampage Mode, greatly increasing her speed.

SkillDec.SourceString: 弗丽嘉进入极限状态，所有行动速度获得提升，会在脚下地面留下霜冻，碰到霜冻的玩家会受到伤害并被减速，最高叠加3层。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frigg enters Extreme Mode, increasing her speed and leaving frost under her feet. If you touch the frost, you will take damage and be slowed, which can be stacked up to 3 times.

SkillDec.SourceString: 瓦尔基里所有行动速度提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Increase speed of all of Valkyrie's actions.

SkillDec.SourceString: 瓦尔基里每秒可以免疫一次伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Valkyrie is immune to damage 1 time every second.

SkillDec.SourceString: 瓦尔基里每隔一段时间会在自身周围地面留下可以被破坏的电极，电极每隔一定时间会对范围内释放圆形电流。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Valkyrie leaves destructible electrodes on the ground around it at regular intervals. These electrodes periodically emit a circular electrical current in the surrounding area.

SkillDec.SourceString: 每隔一段时间，瓦尔基里会对周围降下落雷，落雷会造成致命伤害，并且进入感电状态，感电状态受到雷属性攻击命中会触电。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Valkyrie summons lightning bolts around it at regular intervals, dealing lethal damage and electrifying targets. When an electrified target is hit by a volt attack, chain lightning is triggered.

SkillDec.SourceString: 科尔顿每秒会对选中目标触发敌意，每层敌意使目标减速，最多叠加5层，持续5秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Culton triggers Hostility on the selected target every second. Each stack of Hostility slows the target for 5 seconds, stacking up to 5 times.

SkillDec.SourceString: 科尔顿每隔30秒使周围玩家陷入混乱往反向移动，持续15秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: For every 30 seconds, Culton induces chaos, reversing Wanderers' movement for 15 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 科尔顿每损失10%最大生命值进入3秒无敌状态。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Culton enters an invincible state for 3s each time he loses a certain amount of HP.

SkillDec.SourceString: 科尔顿最终阶段会召唤红色石柱，每个石柱会给科尔顿增加20%增伤和减伤，可让科尔顿撞毁石柱让增益失效。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: In the final phase, Culton summons red pillars. Each pillar increases Culton's damage boost and damage reduction by 20%. Make Culton collide with the pillars to disable the buffs.

SkillDec.SourceString: 铁俑攻击有一定概率给目标添加5秒破招效果，破招效果内霸体失效。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Iron Tomb's attacks have a certain chance to inflict a 5-second Countermove effect, disabling the target's hyperbody for its duration.

SkillDec.SourceString: 铁俑每隔20秒会获得自身损失的最大生命值减伤，持续20秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 20 seconds, Iron Tomb gains damage reduction based on its Max HP lost for 20 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 铁俑每8秒攻击附带一次致残效果，命中非坚毅目标大幅降低其伤害和被治疗效果，持续8秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 8 seconds, Iron Tomb's attacks inflict a Maim effect, significantly reducing the damage dealt and healing received on non-Fortitude targets for 8 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 铁俑每20秒会随机对范围内2名玩家进行链接，被链接的玩家降低30%最终伤害并且每个提供铁俑30%最终伤害，远离铁俑可中断链接。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 20 seconds, Iron Tomb randomly links 2 players within range, reducing their final damage by 30%; each linked player provides a 30% increase in Iron Tomb's final damage. Moving away from Iron Tomb can break the link.

SkillDec.SourceString: 盖亚每次命中非坚毅目标会给目标添加碎骨状态，碎骨叠加到20层会触发骨折，极大降低造成的伤害，持续10秒
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Gaia inflicts Bonecrush on targets without Fortitude with each hit. At 20 stacks, the debuff triggers Cripple, massively reducing their damage dealt for 10s.

SkillDec.SourceString: 盖亚每15秒会随机点名一个目标，该目标5秒后每秒对大范围内除自己外友军造成多次致命伤害。持续5秒
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 15 seconds, Gaia randomly selects a target. After 5 seconds, the selected target inflicts wide-area lethal damage every second to all allies except themselves for 5 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 被盖亚命中后会被减速，最多叠加2层，持续5秒
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Targets hit by Gaia are slowed for 5 seconds, stacking up to 2 times.

SkillDec.SourceString: 盖亚被破盾后10秒内每秒会对周围造成大范围的伤害，被该伤害命中后会叠加15%易伤，最多3层，持续10秒
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Gaia deals wide-area damage every second for 10s after the shield is shattered. Targets hit are inflicted with 15% Vulnerability for 10s, up to 3 stacks.

SkillDec.SourceString: 丝薇缇每25秒会对周围随机2-4个目标释放罚站，BUFF持续5秒后若目标正在进行任何行为则会造成伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 25 seconds, Sweetie casts Penalty on 2–4 random nearby targets. The targets will take damage if they engage in any actions within 5 seconds of receiving Penalty.

SkillDec.SourceString: 丝薇缇所有行动速度提升，并且周围所有目标行动速度下降。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Increase Sweetie's movement speed, and decrease the movement speed of all nearby targets.

SkillDec.SourceString: 丝薇缇每15秒随机选择场上一名目标使其每秒受到巨大伤害（优先选择坚毅目标），持续15秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 15 seconds, Sweetie randomly selects a target on the field to inflict massive damage every second for 15 seconds, prioritizing targets with Fortitude Resonance.

SkillDec.SourceString: 丝薇缇会链接场上所有我方目标，每个目标会损失其他目标受到伤害百分比伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Sweetie chains all Wanderer-allied targets on the field. Each target will suffer damage proportional to the percentage of damage received by other chained targets.

SkillDec.SourceString: 姹鲛每损失一定生命值，攻击力将会获得提高。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Whenever Merbelle loses a certain amount of HP, its attack will increase.

SkillDec.SourceString: 姹鲛拥有护盾时获得高额减伤，并且护盾值大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: When Merbelle has a shield, gain additional damage reduction and greatly increase shield strength.

SkillDec.SourceString: 姹鲛每次伤害添加急冻状态，当累计15层急冻状态会清除急冻状态并大幅减速，持续6秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Each time Merbelle deals damage, inflicts a stack of Flashfreeze. When Flashfreeze stacks 15 times, stacks clear and the Wanderer is greatly slowed for 6 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 姹鲛每隔15秒会对一个目标释放冰柱造成巨大伤害，冰柱会停留在场上，每隔10秒回复姹鲛3%最大生命值，冰柱可通过多次攻击摧毁。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Merbelle unleashes an ice pillar at a target every 15 seconds, dealing huge damage. The ice pillar remains on the field, restoring 3% of Merbelle's Max HP every 10 seconds. The ice pillar can be destroyed by multiple attacks.

SkillDec.SourceString: 急冻机甲周围会持续生成立场生成器，每个生成器给急冻机甲提供减伤，可以通过多次攻击击破。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frost Bot continuously generates positioning generators around it. Each generator provides damage reduction to Frost Bot and can be shattered through multiple attacks.

SkillDec.SourceString: 急冻机甲会对自身进行修复，缓慢回复生命值。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frost Bot will repair itself, slowly recovering HP.

SkillDec.SourceString: 大幅提升急冻机甲行动速度。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Greatly increase the movement speed of Frost Bot.

SkillDec.SourceString: 急冻机甲每秒会对自身周围释放强力寒气，并持续减速周围目标。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frost Bot releases a powerful chill around itself every second, continuously Slowing nearby targets.

SkillDec.SourceString: 攻击附带强力灰噬效果，需要提高对应元素抗性或避免被命中。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Attacks come with a powerful Graying Bite effect. Increase corresponding elemental resistance or avoid being hit.

SkillDec.SourceString: 阿波菲斯变为处决机制，可用破盾高的武器对其破盾并处决。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Apophis can be executed. Use weapons with high shatter to break its shield and execute it.

SkillDec.SourceString: 大幅提升阿波菲斯行动速度。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Greatly increase the movement speed of Apophis.

SkillDec.SourceString: 阿波菲斯周围目标霸体失效。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Nullify the hyperbody status of targets around Apophis.

SkillDec.SourceString: 米诺陶极大降低受到来自主仇恨目标的伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Minotaur significantly reduces damage received from the primary aggro target.

SkillDec.SourceString: 米诺陶变为处决机制，可用破盾高的武器对其破盾并处决。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Minotaur can be executed. Use weapons with high shatter to break its shield and execute it.

SkillDec.SourceString: 米诺陶每隔15秒会随机一个恩赐目标添加毒奶状态，使目标治疗变为同等的伤害。持续10秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 15 seconds, Minotaur randomly selects a target with Benediction, applying Toxicitea, which converts the target's healing into an equivalent amount of damage. Lasts for 10 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 米诺陶每隔15秒会对所有玩家释放检测，若有玩家周围5米内没有其他玩家，该玩家将去除霸体和无敌状态并在90秒内无法添加霸体和无敌状态。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 15 seconds, Minotaur examines all Wanderers. If a Wanderer is found to be within 5 meters without any other Wanderers nearby, that Wanderer will lose their hyperbody and invincibility and will be unable to regain hyperbody or invincibility for 90 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 伦迪尔护盾值大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Greatly increase Rudolph's Shield.

SkillDec.SourceString: 伦迪尔正面获得极大减伤，但背后受到的伤害会提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Rudolph receives a massive damage reduction from the front, but its damage taken from behind is increased.

SkillDec.SourceString: 伦迪尔每隔一定时间会开启5秒大范围幻时。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Rudolph activates a wide-area Phantasia for 5 seconds at set intervals.

SkillDec.SourceString: 伦迪尔开启狂化模式，所有行动速度大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Rudolph enters Rampage Mode, greatly increasing its movement speed.

SkillDec.SourceString: 赛拉芙攻击附带强力灰噬效果。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Seraph's attacks carry an additional Powerful Graying Bite effect.

SkillDec.SourceString: 赛拉芙命中目标后会给15米范围内所有己方单位添加5%最大生命值的生命护盾，无法叠加，持续3秒，最短触发间隔1秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: After Seraph lands a hit on a target, it grants a HP shield to all its friendly units equal to 5% of their respective Max HP. The shield cannot be stacked and lasts for 3 seconds. The minimum trigger interval is 1 second.

SkillDec.SourceString: 赛拉芙命中非坚毅目标后添加制裁，制裁5秒会减少一层，若制裁达到10层则去除霸体和无敌状态并在90秒内无法添加霸体和无敌状态。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: After Seraph hits a non-Fortitude target, Punishments will be added. Punishments will be reduced by 1 stack every 5 seconds. If Punishment stacks reach 10, that Wanderer will lose their hyperbody and invincibility and will be unable to regain hyperbody or invincibility for 90 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 赛拉芙受到致命伤会无敌10秒，并在期间每秒对周围持续造成巨大伤害。触发间隔120秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: When Seraph recevies lethal damage, it becomes invincible for 10 seconds. During that period, it continuously deals a huge amount of damage every second to the surrounding area. The trigger interval is 120 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 索贝克锁定的目标将大幅降低暴击率。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: When Sobek locks onto a target, their critical hit rate is significantly reduced.

SkillDec.SourceString: 索贝克变为处决机制，可用破盾高的武器对其破盾并处决。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Sobek can be executed. Use weapons with high shatter to break its shield and execute it.

SkillDec.SourceString: 索贝克命中非坚毅目标会给目标添加易伤，持续10秒，最多10层。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: When Sobek hits a non-Fortitude target, it applies Vulnerability to the target for 10 seconds, stacking up to 10 times.

SkillDec.SourceString: 索贝克开进入疯狂状态，所有行动速度大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Sobek enters a frenzy state, greatly increasing all speeds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 歌者造成伤害为侵蚀伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: The Singer's attacks inflict Corrosion DMG.

SkillDec.SourceString: 歌者持续对周围造成高额辐射伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: The Singer constantly deals massive Radiation DMG to nearby enemies.

SkillDec.SourceString: 歌者每30秒会身边召唤出一个替身，替身存在时歌者将进入无敌状态。对替身攻击一定次数可消灭替身解除歌者无敌。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: The Singer summons a decoy every 30 seconds, becoming invincible while the decoy exists. Attack the decoy a set number of times to destroy it and dispel the Singer's Invincibility.

SkillDec.SourceString: 歌者每次造成伤害会添加腐蚀效果，腐蚀达到20层会降低目标攻击力和行动速度，持续15秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Whenever dealing damage, the Singer inflicts a stack of Corruption, which, upon reaching 20 stacks, reduces the target's ATK and movement speed for 15 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 耶梦加得所有行为获得加速。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Jormungand gains speed in all actions.

SkillDec.SourceString: 耶梦加得直接斩杀血量低于20%的目标。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Jormungand instantly executes target with less than 20% health.

SkillDec.SourceString: 耶梦加得每隔10秒会对场上所有目标发射穿透光波造成伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 10 seconds, Jormungand fires a piercing light beam, dealing damage to all targets on the field.

SkillDec.SourceString: 耶梦加得自身以及周围怪物受到攻击有概率不会受到伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: There's a chance that Jormungand and nearby monsters won't take damage when attacked.

SkillDec.SourceString: 鬣狗机甲每次攻击会获得一层20%伤害提升过热值，到达5层后会清除过热值回复自己一部分最大生命值。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Hyena Mech gains a 20% damage increase and one stack of Overheat with each attack. Upon reaching 5 Overheat stacks, it resets and restores a portion of its Max HP.

SkillDec.SourceString: 鬣狗机甲的攻击无视目标抗性
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Hyena Mech's attacks ignore the target's resistance.

SkillDec.SourceString: 鬣狗机甲每隔20秒使周围目标生命护盾失效，持续10秒
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Hyena Mech disables the HP shields of surrounding targets every 20s, lasting 10s.

SkillDec.SourceString: 鬣狗机甲会频繁使用机枪扫射，并且扫射范围大幅提升
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Hyena Mech frequently unleashes machine gun sweeps, with its range greatly increased.

SkillDec.SourceString: 南音攻击会随着时间不断提升，受到成功反击后提升攻击将清空。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Nan Yin's ATK increases over time. Successful counterattacks from enemies remove the ATK increased.

SkillDec.SourceString: 南音每隔5秒会使选中目标眩晕2秒，若目标位坚毅则不生效。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Nan Yin stuns the selected target for 2 seconds every 5 seconds, ineffective against targets with Fortitude.

SkillDec.SourceString: 南音额外获得一定减伤，但若被破防会损失大量生命值。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Nan Yin gains additional Damage Reduction, but loses a large amount of HP if shattered.

SkillDec.SourceString: 南音命中目标后会使目标霸体失效，持续10秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Nan Yin negates the target's hyperbody for 10 seconds upon hit.

SkillDec.SourceString: 阿斯拉达每隔一定时间会减少自己受到的伤害，若被破招则减伤会消失。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Asurada periodically gains damage reduction, which is removed when successfully countered.

SkillDec.SourceString: 阿斯拉达命中的目标会降低最大生命值，可叠加3层，持续10秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: When Asurada hits targets, it reduces their Max HP for 10s, stacking up to 3 times.

SkillDec.SourceString: 阿斯拉达命中的目标短时间内无法被治疗。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Asurada prevents targets hit from healing for a short period.

SkillDec.SourceString: 阿斯拉达命中非坚毅目标会对目标进行焚烧，每秒造成百分比最大生命流失，可叠加3层，持续10秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Asurada's hits on non-Fortitude targets sear them, dealing damage based on a percentage of their Max HP every second for 10s, stacking up to 3 times.

SkillDec.SourceString: 巢母拥有较高抗暴能力，若被破防则抗暴能力暂时消失。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: The Hive Mother has high Crit Resistance. If her defenses are shattered, her Crit Resistance will temporarily disappear.

SkillDec.SourceString: 巢母进入战斗会召唤2只狂暴刑徒协助作战，刑徒处于无敌状态，巢母被击败后刑徒会死亡。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Upon entering battle, the Hive Mother will summon 2 Rampage Prisoners to assist in combat. The Prisoners are in an invincible state, and will die once the Hive Mother is defeated.

SkillDec.SourceString: 巢母每隔5秒对锁定目标每秒造成致命伤害，若目标是坚毅则大幅降低该伤害，持续5秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 5 seconds, the Hive Mother inflicts lethal damage every second to the locked-on target for 5 seconds. If the target has Fortitude, this damage is significantly reduced.

SkillDec.SourceString: 巢母每隔15秒检测周围，若周围没有同时存在强攻，均衡，坚毅，恩赐，则巢母所有攻击附带致命伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Every 15 seconds, the Hive Mother scans her surroundings. If Attack, Balance, Fortitude, and Benediction are not present at the same time, all of the Hive Mother's attacks will inflict lethal damage.

SkillDec.SourceString: 孤臣所有攻击额外造成生命百分比伤害，冷却3秒
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Forlorn Minister's attacks deal additional DMG based on the HP ratio. Cooldown: 3 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 孤臣每隔一段时间会进入一小段无敌时间
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Forlorn Minister periodically gains a brief period of invincibility.

SkillDec.SourceString: 孤臣所有行动速度获得一定提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Forlorn Minister temporarily gains increased movement speed.

SkillDec.SourceString: 孤臣护盾将几乎无法被击破。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Forlorn Minister's shield becomes nearly unbreakable.

SkillDec.SourceString: 攻击附带强力灰噬效果，需要提高对应元素抗性或避免被命中。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Attacks come with a powerful Graying Bite effect. Increase corresponding elemental resistance or avoid being hit.

SkillDec.SourceString: BOSS生命血量越低减伤越高，BOSS变为处决机制，可用破盾高的武器对其破盾并处决，处决伤害无视怪物减伤，并与攻击和抗性和增伤有关。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: The lower the boss's HP, the greater its damage reduction. The boss can then be executed. Use weapons with high shatter to break its shield and execute it. Execution damage ignores the boss's damage reduction and is affected by the Wanderer's ATK, resistance, and damage boost.

SkillDec.SourceString: 获得地狱烈焰技能，大部分攻击会在地面留下大面积持续燃烧，避免进入燃烧区域。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Gain the Infernal Flames skill. The majority of the boss's attacks will leave a large area on the ground that burns continuously. Avoid entering the burning areas.

SkillDec.SourceString: 场景随机生成大爆破，被命中会造成致命伤害，并在区域留下地狱烈焰。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Large random explosions will occur in the area, dealing lethal damage upon hit and leaving Infernal Flames in the area.

SkillDec.SourceString: 弗丽嘉护盾值大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frigg's shield strength greatly increases.

SkillDec.SourceString: 弗丽嘉每次命中玩家获得伤害提升，可叠加。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frigg gains a damage boost each time she lands a hit. This effect can stack.

SkillDec.SourceString: 弗丽嘉开启狂暴模式，所有行动速度大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frigg enters Rampage Mode, greatly increasing her speed.

SkillDec.SourceString: 弗丽嘉进入极限状态，所有行动速度获得提升，会在脚下地面留下霜冻，碰到霜冻的玩家会受到伤害并被减速，最高叠加3层。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Frigg enters Extreme Mode, increasing her speed and leaving frost under her feet. If you touch the frost, you will take damage and be slowed, which can be stacked up to 3 times.

SkillDec.SourceString: 瓦尔基里所有行动速度提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Increase speed of all of Valkyrie's actions.

SkillDec.SourceString: 瓦尔基里每秒可以免疫一次伤害。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Valkyrie is immune to damage 1 time every second.

SkillDec.SourceString: 瓦尔基里每隔一段时间会在自身周围地面留下可以被破坏的电极，电极每隔一定时间会对范围内释放圆形电流。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Valkyrie leaves destructible electrodes on the ground around it at regular intervals. These electrodes periodically emit a circular electrical current in the surrounding area.

SkillDec.SourceString: 每隔一段时间，瓦尔基里会对周围降下落雷，落雷会造成致命伤害，并且进入感电状态，感电状态受到雷属性攻击命中会触电。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Valkyrie summons lightning bolts around it at regular intervals, dealing lethal damage and electrifying targets. When an electrified target is hit by a volt attack, chain lightning is triggered.

SkillDec.SourceString: 孤臣所有攻击额外造成生命百分比伤害，冷却3秒
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Forlorn Minister's attacks deal additional DMG based on the HP ratio. Cooldown: 3 seconds.

SkillDec.SourceString: 孤臣每隔一段时间会进入一小段无敌时间
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Forlorn Minister periodically gains a brief period of invincibility.

SkillDec.SourceString: 孤臣所有行动速度获得一定提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Forlorn Minister temporarily gains increased movement speed.

SkillDec.SourceString: 孤臣护盾将几乎无法被击破。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Forlorn Minister's shield becomes nearly unbreakable.

SkillDec.SourceString: 刑天生命值低于25%会对周围造成一次伤害并进入15秒无敌，该效果只会触发一次。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Xingtian deals damage once to nearby enemies and gains invicibility for 15s when HP drops below 25%. Triggers only once.

SkillDec.SourceString: 刑天对比自己生命百分比高的目标造成的伤害大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Xingtian deals significantly increased damage to targets with a higher HP ratio than himself.

SkillDec.SourceString: 刑天命中非坚毅目标有概率大幅降低目标所有行动速度，持续4秒。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Xingtian has a chance to significantly reduce the movement speed of non-Fortitude targets for 4s when hitting them.

SkillDec.SourceString: 刑天所有行动速度大幅提升。
SkillDec.LocalizedString: Xingtian significantly increases his movement speed.
